==English==
===Noun===
'''attrition'''
# wearing or grinding down by [[friction]]
# (military) A gradual, natural reduction in membership or personnel, as through retirement, resignation, or [[death]]
# A policy of decruitment by not recruiting following voluntary resignation or retirement.


====Translations====
*French: [[usure]] (par friction) (f) (1), départs volontaires (m) (2, 3)

